# DOWNLOADING
----------------------------

Download new versions from:

Program modification dates will appear on the web page.
Please check the modification history of milos.pro.

----------------------------
# COMPATIBILITY
----------------------------

IDL 6.0 and superior (not tested in earlier versions)

----------------------------
# INSTALLATION
----------------------------

tar -zxvf <archive>.tar.gz

Program files should be placed in your IDL PATH.

Example (in IDL> or .idl_startup): 

!path=!path+':'+expand_path("+/Users/orozco/IDL/Synthesis/Milos_idl_beta1.2/")

Use any method you like.

Run the test program -> test.pro

